{"tid":1446680,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急】明日(12/8)黑警記者會問題集中串","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:02:36.000Z","uid":261582,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d0aa8c3f091111abe7eea343a283ae3c5688cb66","tid":1446680,"uid":261582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:12:51.000Z","msg":"下次記者會要問咩喺度留低<br />\n集思廣益<br />\n大家諗下有咩核心問題必問<br />\n等記者行家唔洗追咁多post<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"206a68936e100783f1b1d383f337afc5b6e80e7b","tid":1446680,"uid":261582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:13:06.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"d7d8608ff2bf9c297a3288d9f2f7cb2b03b4de91","tid":1446680,"uid":261582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:15:35.000Z","msg":"委任證"},{"pid":"f9d9a74f845e1d44bdc43d40ae83bb4f389d8518","tid":1446680,"uid":1315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:16:09.000Z","msg":"記得追問 唔好比佢地隨便帶過 9up"},{"pid":"2198725257c7ee275456e8ac3493ef29de2c4bf9","tid":1446680,"uid":261582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:17:43.000Z","msg":"放竹插贓嫁禍"},{"pid":"dc40bb1c4e6ec02d26e9928062836865c5cfc95b","tid":1446680,"uid":261582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:18:22.000Z","msg":"黑警公信力"},{"pid":"bce12ef78bea594044ff250199077b84e3dbeeed","tid":1446680,"uid":261582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:20:10.000Z","msg":"前言不對後語<br />\n街道狹窄唔批不反對<br />\n但係自己又喺啲咁狹窄嘅地方放催淚"},{"pid":"8ad347d47c32d16f69a32b5daf9f7a1c06ba8f84","tid":1446680,"uid":261582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:21:30.000Z","msg":"警員疑似不能自控<br />\n要Commander企喺佢前面先識停"},{"pid":"4245179b785782a5688bb51c01b1d74ef0e4924c","tid":1446680,"uid":261582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:23:42.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"aaf20ee6bbd96cec81a8f1ed166bde7856d7e3a3","tid":1446680,"uid":261582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:25:41.000Z","msg":"係咪一有示威<br />\n就會唔夠警力<br />\n跟住全港就無法律"},{"pid":"939abf45e7ca1995590f85daa974c473f89788f0","tid":1446680,"uid":261582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQZURP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQZURP7.jpg&h=e8ff53ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BvexDu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvexDu8.jpg&h=6025e5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnQpuBP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnQpuBP.jpg&h=bdc91acf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Product should only be used outdoors. <br />\n<br />\nDo not fire directly at personnel</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記者會上話會跟足廠商指引而無必要親身試彈，宜家冇跟指引就有必要親身試啦？</span><br />\n<br />\n間廠叫NonLethal Technology, 有冇人去提醒下間廠再培訓垃圾狗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nonlethaltechnologies.com%2F&d=rP1lJsqA2sO3Td0%2BA1LJ5wy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=35b4a014\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/</a>"},{"pid":"a53df4d6285a72ac6f10679baa61317474e07830","tid":1446680,"uid":285112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:28:25.000Z","msg":"1) 點解太古站可以喺無警告之下突然施放催淚彈？究竟警察嘅戰術目標係驅散示威者定係要佢地人踩人或者碌落樓梯？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2) 有影片拍到警察喺警署內換晒黑衫先出街、扮示威者喺黃大仙拋爆竹、喺深水涉跟蹤浸大學生會主席去買雷射筆、喺銅鑼灣當街黑衣警員拘捕黑衣示威者等等。亦有警隊內部訊息流出，話由7月1日開始，已有警察著黑衫混入假扮示威者群挑動情緒。<br />\n警方而家同以後，點去證明其他嘅暴力行為，的而且確唔係臥底警員所為？<br />\n<br />\nP.S. <br />\nfr friend:<br />\nIVE警察朋友睇唔過眼<br />\n終於爆料由7月1日後已經派警察扮示威者，但係班前線一直唔知。<br />\n之前掟汽油彈 掟磚頭的 大部分都係警察扮既。目的想增加社會對示威者既仇恨，令社會轉風向。<br />\n另外之前有部分示威者俾人捉，都係警察扮，目的係想示威者滅聲，唔敢再出黎。<br />\n今日因爲係銅鑼灣俾示威者發現身分，所以唯有表明身分將佢地拘捕。"},{"pid":"993133d33c3d6b2d08960ee32362efd814214054","tid":1446680,"uid":261582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:30:22.000Z","msg":"警察帶頭暴動可能性"},{"pid":"b5597b3ff857420d44dc329e501c764b7025dfcc","tid":1446680,"uid":261582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:39:12.000Z","msg":"聯同黑社會向市民發動恐怖襲擊"},{"pid":"2bd19e5c41c56160b3e95f9a5aa70969dd2b4a44","tid":1446680,"uid":261582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:43:14.000Z","msg":"1. 警方不依指引對示威者使用高殺傷力武器，八月十一日令一位女示威者眼球爆裂失去全部視力<br />\n2. 721沒有一位施襲者被起訴<br />\n3. 警方扮示威者帶領並在現場進行所有犯法行為<br />\n4. 在密閉空間內施放催淚彈"},{"pid":"7829fdb57b95c51e03f01d71d4807ab5b50efca9","tid":1446680,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:02:36.000Z","msg":"1. 原本示威者想離開現場, 但在場有便衣扮演示威者煽動留低, 攻擊甚至插贓嫁禍比被捕示威者<br />\n2. 室內密閉開槍, 違反廠商指引<br />\n3. 示威者冇攻擊行為, 警察選擇近距離一米開槍攻擊示威者, 甚至引起恐慌險導致人踏人逃跑<br />\n4. 有警察曾公開撰文會HEADSHOT市民, 今次更故意瞄準示威者眼部開槍<br />\n5. 過期催淚神經病氣會產生大量有害氣體, 嚴重違反廠商指引"}]}